<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥkạyẗ ʿdrạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 kạn fy ṣbyẗ mn ṣgẖrạ mlyạnẗ bnʿmẗ ạllh
 ạṣṭfạhạ tbqy̱ ʿdrạ wmjdw fyhạ ytjly̱
 kẖlạ mlạkw lʿndạ yrwḥ ybsẖrhạ bḥlwl ạlrwk
 ykẖbrhạ ạ̉ḥly̱ ḥkạyẗ ʿn ṭfl ṣgẖyr jạyẗ
 qblt mnw sẖw qlạ wṣạrt ʿdrạ ạ̉m ạllh
 ạlbsẖry yạlly qbltyhạ lkl ạlnạs ḥmltyhạ
 klmẗ ạllh ḥfẓtyhạ bqlbk wtạ̉mltyhạ
 ṭwbạk yạ ạ̉m ạlkl tḥt jnạḥk bdnạ nḍl
 kwny mʿnạ wʿynyạ wlmḥbẗ ạllh ạhdynạ
 ḥty̱ nḥml hạlbsẖry̱ mtlk ạ̹nt yạ ʿdrạ</lyrics>
